{"results":[{"aya":"001","id":4847,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"复活时临近了，月亮破裂了。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"002","id":4848,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"如果他们看见一种迹象，他们就退避，而且说：这是一种有力的魔术。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"003","id":4849,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"他们否认他，而且顺从私欲。每一件事都是确定的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"004","id":4850,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"包含警戒的许多消息，确已来临他们了，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"005","id":4851,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"那是极精密的智慧；但警告是无效的，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"006","id":4852,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"故你应当避开他们。当召唤者召人于难事的日子，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"007","id":4853,"locale":"zh","sura":"054","text":"他们不敢仰视地由坟中出来，好象是遍地的蝗虫；","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":8,"nextPage":"/zh/s054-2.json"}}